 The bot crawled from out of a cave. He was completeley destraught and tired. 
He had been through much just to arrive here. His datatracks scrambled he 
could barley remember his name. It was life. A plant beast mode he 
transformed into robot mode and found the strength to fly to what he thought 
was the alliace ship. He collapsed on the front of its ramp towards the 
opening. Sending a destress call....he hoped his fellow maximals would help 
him.
